description: Train is running 2 hours late and the attendant was rude when asked about arrival time.
The toilet in coach B1 is extremely dirty and the pantry served stale food.
I booked ticket online but my name is misspelled. Please correct.
A suspicious bag was left in coach S3. No one is claiming it. Please check immediately.
Passenger in coach A1, seat 23, has severe chest pain. Need medical assistance urgently.
Train delayed by 1 hour at Vijayawada due to signal failure. No announcement made.
The TTE was very uncooperative and spoke rudely.
Coach S5 has cockroaches and dirty linen.
The meal served was cold and tasted bad.
Unable to cancel ticket online, website error.
Train is delayed by 4 hours and a passenger needs insulin which is running out.
Bedrolls in coach A2 are stained and smelly.
The coach attendant was not helpful with luggage.
Lights are flickering in coach S1, possible electrical issue.
The vegetarian meal had a piece of chicken in it.
Duplicate ticket booking charged twice.
Toilets are overflowing and train is running late.
The pantry staff was arguing with passengers.
Passenger fainted in coach B3. Need doctor immediately.
Smoke coming from under seat in coach S2.
Senior citizen concession not applied correctly.
Train delayed by 2 hours due to fog.
Seats are dirty and have food crumbs.
The tea was cold and the samosa was stale.
The TTE asked for bribe to upgrade seat.
Woman in labor in coach S4, need medical help.
Someone tried to pickpocket in crowded coach.
Garbage not collected since morning.
Train delayed by 3 hours due to operational issues.
Refund not processed after cancellation 10 days ago.
The coach attendant was sleeping and didn't respond to calls.
Water leaking from AC vent in coach A3.
Breakfast was not provided even though included in ticket.
Train is delayed and there is no announcement. Passengers are anxious.
Passenger having seizure in coach B2. Need doctor.
E-ticket not received after payment.
Bed bugs in coach S2.
The ticket checker was very rude when asked about seat allocation.
Train is 2 hours late and toilets are locked.
Chain pulling incident in coach S1.
The dinner was very oily and gave me indigestion.
Passenger with asthma having breathing difficulty. Need oxygen.
Dust and dirt all over floor.
Train held at outer signal for 30 minutes without reason.
Unable to book ticket via app, payment failed but amount deducted.
The pantry staff was unhygienic, touched food with bare hands.
Broken glass near door in coach S3, unsafe for children.
Child has high fever and needs paracetamol.
Sink in washbasin is clogged.
Train late by 1 hour and food ran out in pantry.
Wrong coach number printed on ticket.
The cleaning staff was mopping during breakfast time, causing dust.
Foul smell in coach, possibly from bathroom.
Passenger behaving violently, seems mentally disturbed.
Train delayed due to track maintenance.
The packaged water bottle tasted like chemicals.
Spilled tea on seat, not cleaned for hours.
The guard was not available for complaint registration.
Elderly passenger fell and hurt leg, needs first aid.
Rat seen in coach, passengers scared.
Name mismatch due to typo in ticket.
Train stopped for 45 minutes due to cattle on track.
Litter everywhere, no dustbin in coach.
The meal was served cold and had a hair in it.
The TTE refused to help with luggage for an elderly passenger.
Passenger having heart attack, need immediate medical assistance.
Door not closing properly in coach A1.
Train late and toilets are dirty and without water.
Cannot download ticket PDF from website.
The pantry staff was very rude and overcharged.
Train is 3 hours late and a diabetic passenger needs food urgently.
Mice droppings found near seat in coach B3.
The puri was undercooked and doughy.
Passenger smoking in coach, no action by staff.
Refund for cancelled train not credited after 15 days.
Coach not cleaned since starting and staff ignored requests.
Pregnant woman in coach S2 has severe pain, need doctor.
Train delayed by 2 hours due to technical snag.
The soup was served cold and tasted sour.
Fire extinguisher missing in coach B2.
The attendant was using phone while on duty and ignored calls.
Train stranded due to flood, need food and water for passengers.
Spider webs in corners of coach.
E-ticket has wrong date.
